{"by":"perplexa","id":47750228,"kids":[47750317],"parent":47742200,"text":"Hi there! I really like this project and just bought a copy for myself.<p>It would be great to allow offline activation - as others have pointed out, using the application after the activation servers may go away is something that is useful for an application like this.<p>Also, the application viewer seems a bit clunky - please allow sorting pinned items via drag &amp; drop, or always sort them alphabetically. A mouse over highlight effect is also missing.","time":1776077386,"type":"comment"}